'''Tim Dry''' is a mime artist who portrayed [[J'Quille/Legends|J'Quille]] and a [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]] officer in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]. In his book entitled ''Continuum -The Star Wars Phenomenon As Experienced From The Inside'', he recounts being in one of the biggest-grossing movies of all time.<ref name="SWI" />

